# Armbian virtual ARM64 image for qemu
#
#
# produces a single partition VM image in qcow2 format.
# how to use
# the resulting cache/sources/u-boot/v22021.04/u-boot.bin will need to be copied.. that is your bios
# how to run on linux
##!/bin/bash
#
